    GenericObserver<ArgumentType>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CircleFinderThread
    Searches in a given image-file for circles.
    FileCircleFindingsPair
    A pair of an image and a list of circles which where found in the image.
    GenericObservable<ArgumentType>  
    GmapsCoordinateCircleFindingsPair
    A pair of an image and a list of circles which where found in the image extended with the coordinate of the image.
    MapDigesterCircleFinder  
    MapDigesterCircleFinder.MapDigesterCircleFinderParameter
    An Class for holding parameter-values for the MapDigesterCircleFinderThread
    MapDigesterCircleFinderThread
    Finds circles in a given image.
    MapDigesterLocator<CircleFindingsPairType extends craj.mapDigesterLocator.CircleFindingsPair>
    This abstract class implements the functionality of creating as much as CircleFinderThread objects as processor cores are available.
    MapDigesterLocator.MapDigesterLocatorParameter
    This class holds the parameter data for the MapDigesterLocator
    MapDigesterLocatorForFiles
    This class extends the MapDigesterLocator for the functionality to get all files from the given directory and starts the search for circles of these files.
    MapDigesterLocatorForGMaps
    This class extends the MapDigesterLocator for the functionality to get all images from Google Maps in the specified range between the given longitude and latitude.
    MapDigesterLocatorForGMaps.MapDigesterLocatorForGMapsParameter
    This class holds the parameter data for the MapDigesterLocatorForGMaps
